WEBVTT

00:05:58.480 --> 00:06:00.216
Zinadan tushdim va

00:06:00.240 --> 00:06:02.456
stol ortida o’tirgan gavdali 
kishini ko’rdim.

00:06:02.480 --> 00:06:04.216
U qo’riqchiga o’xshab ko’rindi.

00:06:04.240 --> 00:06:05.776
Shu sababdan unga yaqinlashdim.

00:06:05.800 --> 00:06:07.536
Yurib boryapman

00:06:07.560 --> 00:06:09.896
va bu umrimdagi eng uzun yo’l edi,
bo'ynimning

00:06:09.920 --> 00:06:12.056
orqa qismidagi
tuklar tik holatda,

00:06:12.080 --> 00:06:14.536
terlayotgandim, yuragim
esa gupirlab urardi.

00:06:14.560 --> 00:06:15.776
Borib shunday dedim

00:06:15.800 --> 00:06:18.456
“Hoy, janob 100 dollar
qarz bera olasizmi?”

00:06:18.480 --> 00:06:19.816
(Kulgu)

00:06:19.840 --> 00:06:21.640
U menga qarab “Yo’q.”

00:06:22.640 --> 00:06:23.840
“Nega?” dedi

00:06:24.200 --> 00:06:26.496
Men esa “Yo’qmi? Kechirasiz.” dedim.
So'ng esa

00:06:26.520 --> 00:06:28.235
orqamga o’girilib,
qochib qoldim.

00:06:28.259 --> 00:06:29.619
(Kulgu)